      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我們來畫一個語音翻譯系統的狀態圖吧。核心流程是從 WorkerNode 啟動後進入 Idle，使用者按下錄音按鈕就進到 Recording 狀態。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Idle",
