    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，Idle 到 Recording 的觸發條件是「按下錄音按鈕」對吧？那如果使用者中途取消錄音，要直接回到 Idle 嗎？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Recording"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "對，取消就回 Idle，同時要清理資源。錄音結束後進入 Processing，這裡會做 ASR 和翻譯。對了，Processing 之後有兩條分支：TTS 啟用就進 Playing，停用就直接回 Idle 顯示文字結果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recording",
        "Processing",
        "Playing",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把主流程畫出來。另外我注意到 Processing 可能會失敗，是不是需要一個 Error 狀態來承接？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "沒錯，Error 要連回 Idle 讓使用者確認後清除。但還有一個嚴重錯誤的情況，要直接導向 IngressController 做系統終止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Playing 結束後也是回到 Idle 重置狀態吧？還有使用者中斷播放的情況？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Playing",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
